OL,3,CMan who caused head-on crash after
OL,4,Cdriving on wrong side of the road is
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FWatch: Footage shows Dias on the wrong
OL,8,Fside of the road and the aftermath of
OL,9,Fthe crash which left a man with life-
OL,10,Fchanging injuries
OL,12,FA 'careless and dangerous' driver who
OL,13,Fcaused a head-on crash, leaving
OL,14,Fanother driver with life-changing
OL,15,Finjuries, has been jailed.
OL,17,FIn January last year, Jean Dias was
OL,18,Fdriving a Land Rover on the wrong side
OL,19,Fof the A21 near Robertsbridge in
OL,20,FSussex, when he collided with a white
OL,21,FFord Fiesta.
