OL,3,CMan who caused head-on crash after
OL,4,Cdriving on wrong side of the road is
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FThe other driver, a 54-year-old man
OL,8,Ffrom Hastings, had to be cut free from
OL,9,Fthe wreckage and has suffered life-
OL,10,Fchanging injuries.
OL,12,FWhen Dias spoke to police, he claimed
OL,13,Fthere must have been a vehicle fault
OL,14,Fthat caused his car to veer to the
OL,15,Fright. But an investigation found
OL,16,Fthere were no defects on the car.
