OL,3,CMan who caused head-on crash after
OL,4,Cdriving on wrong side of the road is
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FFootage was shown to a court which
OL,8,Fcaptures Dias' vehicle travelling on
OL,9,Fthe wrong side of the road for at
OL,10,Fleast ten seconds leading up to the
OL,11,Fcrash.
OL,13,FThe 44-year-old, formerly a company
OL,14,Fdirector, admitted causing serious
OL,15,Finjury by dangerous driving.
OL,17,FOn 19 April, He was jailed for two
OL,18,Fyears and four months, and has been
OL,19,Fdisqualified from driving for five
OL,20,Fyears.
