OL,3,CMan who caused head-on crash after
OL,4,Cdriving on wrong side of the road is
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,F"It illustrates the danger of not
OL,8,Fpaying full attention when you're
OL,9,Fbehind the wheel.
OL,11,F"We may never know the full reason why
OL,12,FDias was on the wrong side of the
OL,13,Froad, but it was most likely a
OL,14,Fsignificant and prolonged lapse in
OL,15,Fconcentration.
OL,17,F"Dias is fortunate that this collision
OL,18,Fdid not lead to the death of the
OL,19,Fdriver in the Ford Fiesta, or to more
OL,20,Fserious harm for himself and other
OL,21,Froad users.
