OL,7,F"Throughout April my colleagues across
OL,8,Fthe Roads Policing Unit have been
OL,9,Fcarrying out additional patrols to
OL,10,Fraise awareness of the 'fatal five'
OL,11,Ffactors which cause people to be
OL,12,Fkilled or seriously injured on our
OL,13,Froads.
OL,15,F"Those factors are; driving at excess
OL,16,For inappropriate speed, drink or drug-
OL,17,Fdriving, not wearing a seatbelt,
OL,18,Fdriving while distracted such as using
OL,19,Fa mobile phone, and driving in a
OL,20,Fcareless, anti-social or dangerous
OL,21,Fmanner as in this case.
